a.n: Girls Aloud - Girls Aloud: Tangled Up - Live From The O2

p.d: Britain’s favourite girl band take to the stage for a spectacular live show from London’s O2 Arena in October 2008, with a setlist covering a mix of all the classic Girls Aloud hits from their critically-acclaimed 'Tangled Up' album, with stunning costume changes watch the girls deliver a truly fantastic show at the height of their powers. Includes 'Sexy! No No No', 'Sound Of The Underground', 'Can’t Speak French', 'Jump' and many many more!
